<div class="com-share" data-id="9140" data-title="《「这世界」放弃十万美元年薪去卖冰激凌，这也是生活》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/9140/medium/9140.jpg?1436688099" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/9140.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
